description: Number of partitions of n into parts of 20 kinds.
comments: a(n) is Euler transform of A010859. - _Alois P. Heinz_, Oct 17 2008
links: Index entries for expansions of Product_{k >= 1} (1-x^k)^m
maple: with(numtheory): a:= proc(n) option remember; `if`(n=0, 1, add(add(d*20, d=divisors(j)) *a(n-j), j=1..n)/n) end: seq(a(n), n=0..40); # _Alois P. Heinz_, Oct 17 2008
crossrefs: 20th column of A144064. - _Alois P. Heinz_, Oct 17 2008
author: _David W. Wilson_
